\end_inset

Los cuartiles son tres y se definen:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $Q_{1}=p_{25}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $Q_{2}=p_{50}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
